"description" = "Stop spending hours planning. Beacon builds a complete day-by-day trip in seconds—just tell it where you're going and what you enjoy.\n\nPick a destination, choose your interests, set your budget and pace. Beacon does the rest: a full itinerary with the right sights in the right order, restaurants worked in at the right times, and places to stay that match your style. Every stop lands on a map, so you always know where you're headed next.\n\nHOW IT WORKS\n• Enter your destination and travel dates\n• Choose what you're into—food, history, nightlife, nature, art, and more\n• Set your pace, from a walkable cluster to a wider region with longer drives\n• Pick a budget, from street food and free sights to fine dining and upscale stays\n• Get a day-by-day plan, mapped and ready to go\n\nPLANS THAT ACTUALLY MAKE SENSE\nBeacon plans your days the way you'd actually travel them. Stops are spread across the day, not crammed together. Meals show up when you're hungry, not stacked on top of sights. Each day flows from one place to the next without doubling back.\n\nSEE EVERYTHING ON A MAP\nYour whole trip lives on a map. Tap any stop for details, jump between days with a single swipe, and see exactly how your day connects from morning to night.\n\nEAT WELL\nRestaurants are built into your schedule around real mealtimes—breakfast, lunch, and dinner—matched to your budget and taste, so you're never stuck hungry between sights.\n\nA PLACE TO STAY\nGet accommodation suggestions near your route that fit your budget, so you spend less time searching and more time exploring.\n\nYOUR TRAVEL PASSPORT\nSave the trips you take and the photos you shoot. Build a passport of where you've been—organised by trip and day—so your memories live in one place, not scattered across your camera roll.\n\nDISCOVER MORE\nBrowse points of interest and find new places worth your time, wherever you are.\n\nMADE FOR REAL TRIPS\nWeekend city break or a fortnight's adventure, Beacon adapts to how you travel—your pace, your budget, your interests. No spreadsheets, no twenty browser tabs, no guesswork.\n\nPlan less. Travel more. Download Beacon and get your next trip ready in seconds.\n\n—\n\nTerms of Use:  https://gist.github.com/orangutanger1/3dbdc655861a4fa330194ae396a21f45/raw/620f2ea265477b8afd0cebeedac3f7023eb1a499/TermsOfService.md";
